The '''''Fortune Seeker''''' was a [[Ryn/Legends|Ryn]] [[Starship/Legends|starship]] associated with the [[Ryn Network]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The Ryn used it to move about [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] and gather information.

